00:01:51.000 --> 00:03:13.000
<h1>Disability</h1>
<h2>It can be</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Acquired at birth or result of an event (illness, accident)</li>
  <li>Scalable</li>
  <li>Non permanent</li>
  <li>Accumulative</li>
</ul>
<h2>It is often of origin</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Sensory: functions of perception (sight, hearing ...)</li>
  <li>Motor: ability to perform movements</li>
  <li>Cognitive: brain functions (attention, memory ...)</li>
</ul>
